  113. ‌val operation_is_pure : operation -> bool
  114.   (** Returns [true] if the given operation only produces a result
  115.       in its destination registers, but has no side effects whatsoever:
  116.       it doesn't raise exceptions, it doesn't modify already-allocated
  117.       blocks, it doesn't adjust the stack frame, etc. *)

  119. ‌val operation_can_raise : operation -> bool
